node.title: Here's what is happening as the Queensland border opens to Victoria and NSW
node.description: Queensland's border is officially open to COVID hotspots with up to 50,000 vehicles expected to enter the state today. Follow live.
node.content: ["Queensland's border is officially open to COVID\u00a0hotspots\u00a0with up to 50,000\u00a0vehicles expected to enter the state in the coming days.", "Follow all of Monday's news and updates on our live blog."]
